{"tid":1332802,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"尖沙咀K11 MUSEA新戲院 8月開幕","createTime":"2019-07-19T12:32:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T04:41:17.000Z","uid":283908,"like":17,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"97142a87d7e3bff98530d7b7aac20cdd8b494826","tid":1332802,"uid":283908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T12:32:12.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>UA全新旗艦戲院「K11 Art House」</strong></div><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: left;\"><br />\n戲院地址 ：香港尖沙咀梳士巴利道 18 號 Victoria Dockside K11 MUSEA 4 樓 415 號鋪 （地圖）<br />\n開幕日期 ：2019 年8月</div></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>位於尖沙咀的新商場K11 MUSEA即將於2019第三季開幕！UA亦宣佈全新旗艦影院「K11 Art House」將進駐商場！戲院將會在8月開幕，設有12個影廳，提供1,708座位。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hLncwL3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhLncwL3.jpg&h=e22978d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A8e2TZx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA8e2TZx.jpg&h=3cb31227&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全港首間 IMAX&reg; Laser 影廳</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nK11 Art House為全港首間IMAX&reg;影廳，採用IMAX&reg; Laser放映系統，配合12聲道IMMERSIVE音響系統，為大家帶來更優質的畫質和立體的音效。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BbYOPx6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBbYOPx6.png&h=b3f4d044&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>多功能表演藝術影廳</strong><br />\n另外，K11 Art House設有多功能表演藝術廳，可舉辦各類型的表演和活動。 UA CineHub 亦為 K11 Art House 帶來一系列文化電影，包括：聚焦世界知名藝術家的「ARTiculate」主題電影系列，以及「尋找古典音樂大師」電影系列等，讓觀眾有優質的電影體驗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W5r8Pym.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW5r8Pym.jpg&h=f90c7827&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一共有12 間影廳，提供 1,711 個座位。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Source:</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/968316/lifestyle/weekend-leisure/%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e5%a5%bd%e5%8e%bb%e8%99%95-ua%e6%88%b2%e9%99%a2-%e5%b0%96%e6%b2%99%e5%92%80-k11-musea/3/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.weekendhk.com%2F968316%2Flifestyle%2Fweekend-leisure%2F%25e9%25a6%2599%25e6%25b8%25af%25e5%25a5%25bd%25e5%258e%25bb%25e8%2599%2595-ua%25e6%2588%25b2%25e9%2599%25a2-%25e5%25b0%2596%25e6%25b2%2599%25e5%2592%2580-k11-musea%2F3%2F&d=iVbTvSvdcfz%2Fe2yCQDPMV%2F3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=7ddc015f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.weekendhk.com/968316/lifestyle/weekend-leisure/%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e5%a5%bd%e5%8e%bb%e8%99%95-ua%e6%88%b2%e9%99%a2-%e5%b0%96%e6%b2%99%e5%92%80-k11-musea/3/</a>"},{"pid":"10b71f1d2d192667ad9c852a641787b05f22048a","tid":1332802,"uid":71508,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T12:41:27.000Z","msg":"正imax"},{"pid":"ae8a23a90ccf7df618ddc0917510856acd0d3e20","tid":1332802,"uid":283908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"10b71f1d2d192667ad9c852a641787b05f22048a","tid":1332802,"uid":71508,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T12:41:27.000Z","msg":"正imax"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T12:43:35.000Z","msg":"但最近好似冇咩戲值得睇IMAX...."},{"pid":"ad44baef12139ae35793b670326765ab5013d743","tid":1332802,"uid":71508,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"ae8a23a90ccf7df618ddc0917510856acd0d3e20","tid":1332802,"uid":283908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"10b71f1d2d192667ad9c852a641787b05f22048a","tid":1332802,"uid":71508,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T12:41:27.000Z","msg":"正imax"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T12:43:35.000Z","msg":"但最近好似冇咩戲值得睇IMAX...."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T12:56:57.000Z","msg":"獅子王"},{"pid":"898ec92856812b738d6a2f8b0536eecfb6dc2594","tid":1332802,"uid":283908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad44baef12139ae35793b670326765ab5013d743","tid":1332802,"uid":71508,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"ae8a23a90ccf7df618ddc0917510856acd0d3e20","tid":1332802,"uid":283